    <system:String x:Key="Resource_ShareDialog_InstructionText" xml:space="preserve">To share this deck:
• Read the Terms and Conditions
• Check the I Accept checkbox
• Enter your name in the Sender’s name text box
• Click Share it

When you click the “Share It” button, FlashCards.Show will:
  1. Upload your deck to the cloud service. 
     During the upload you will see some animation. Do not exit the application 
     until the upload is complete. 
  2. Open your default mail client and automatically create an email for you to send
     to those with whom you wish to share this deck.

Note: Remember that you do not control where the deck goes after you send it to your recipients. Do not upload deck files that contain any personal information, pornography, any content that you don’t own, or any other content you don’t want to share beyond the recipients to whom you send it.</system:String>
